text: Lainie is a given name. Notable people with the name include: *Lainie Kazan (born 1940), American actor *Lainie Frasier, American film, television and video-game actor *Lainie Marsh, American singer-songwriter *Lainie Friedman Ross, American physician and bioethicist ==See also== *Lany (disambiguation) *Laney (disambiguation) *Lainey Category:English-language feminine given names
title: Lainie
